data.description: Welcome Home! This beautiful two-story home, 3/2.5/2 has everything you need! The spacious floor plan is great for entertaining all types of crowds. The custom built shiplap is a great bonus as it can hold up to 85” TV. The mock fireplace is a great feature to snuggle with the one you love best during the colder times. Be in your new home before Christmas. Several upgrades have been completed; you won't be disappointed. Call today for your personal tour.
